				<td colspan="2"><span>As a rule, AE DOT songs with dark blue mobs isnt good.  They lead to a vicious circle of death
<br />

<br />
DOTS = Aggro and no mezz.
<br />

<br />
AGGRO = damage
<br />

<br />
DAMAGE = Healing
<br />

<br />
HEALING = Aggro
<br />

<br />
You started it with DOTS.  You cant mezz DOTd mobs till the DOT wears off.  Like Sin said, once the cleric gets aggro, you better either have Kazumi's up, or you better have a warrior with AE taunt and luck.  Your Dots will NOT pull aggro of a healer or slower.</span></td>
