				<td colspan="2"><span>&quot;Ok, this is hypothetical as I've never been so brave to use MoM as crowd control. I'm not discounting your wonderful post, just the use of Mischief.&quot;
<br />

<br />
Give it a try some time, Sin.  It's not something I pull out in a shlub pickup group, but when I'm plowing through normals with a well-geared group of 65s, this works like a dream.  MoM agro is surprisingly low...if the tank's pulling, I can toss one out as the mobs are entering the room and 4 times out of 5 they'll stay on the tank (provided I stand behind him/her and don't go running into the storm).  Despite this it DOES seem to juggle up the hate lists just enough that the healers/slowers get less agro than you'd expect.
<br />

