				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: What do I do when there's a stubborn warrior?<a name="24901"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 2 04 9:53 AM</span></td>
